PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1779185247
OL,3,CNeedle exchange facility plans spark
OL,4,Canti-social behaviour concerns for
OL,5,Ctraders
OL,7,FConcerns have been raised by business
OL,8,Fowners that a new needle exchange
OL,9,Ffacility in Belfast city centre will
OL,10,Fsee them lose trade and bring an
OL,11,Fincrease in anti-social behaviour.
OL,13,FHowever, those in favour said the
OL,14,Fexchange would allow drug users to
OL,15,Ftrade in used needles and would be the
OL,16,Fonly service on offer to help keep
OL,17,Fusers safe.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1779185247
OL,3,CNeedle exchange facility plans spark
OL,4,Canti-social behaviour concerns for
OL,5,Ctraders
OL,7,FAccording to the latest figures by the
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland Research and
OL,9,FStatistics Agency (NIRSA), there were
OL,10,F251 drug related deaths in 2024, with
OL,11,F80 being in Belfast.
OL,13,FBelfast City Council approved plans by
OL,14,Fthe Belfast Trust for a needle
OL,15,Fexchange in December 2025.
OL,17,FOwner of Elliott's Fancy Dress, Clark
OL,18,FElliott said: "We have a massive
OL,19,Famount of people coming over across
OL,20,Fthe bridge every day.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1779185247
OL,3,CNeedle exchange facility plans spark
OL,4,Canti-social behaviour concerns for
OL,5,Ctraders
OL,7,F"Children who live in the area, we
OL,8,Fhave the tourists who use this as a
OL,9,Fkey destination for tourists to come
OL,10,Fand visit, take photographs.
OL,12,F"It's Belfast waterfront, so it
OL,13,Fdoesn't make sense to have a facility
OL,14,Flike this on the waterfront.
OL,16,F"I don't think it's the right place,
OL,17,Fthe right location for it. It will
OL,18,Fdefinitely affect our business, it
OL,19,Fwill affect other businesses in the
OL,20,Fareas.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1779185247
OL,3,CNeedle exchange facility plans spark
OL,4,Canti-social behaviour concerns for
OL,5,Ctraders
OL,7,F"I do feel sympathy for them. They
OL,8,Fshouldn't be left to their own, they
OL,9,Fdo need help. But I don't think it
OL,10,Fshould be done on the streets of
OL,11,FBelfast."
OL,13,FNeedle exchanges work by allowing
OL,14,Fusers to anonymously give in used
OL,15,Fneedles and receive new clean ones.
OL,16,FFor those who have seen them work up
OL,17,Fclose, they help to protect users and
OL,18,Fthe community.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1779185247
OL,3,CNeedle exchange facility plans spark
OL,4,Canti-social behaviour concerns for
OL,5,Ctraders
OL,7,FThe People's Kitchen, Paul McCusker
OL,8,Fsaid: "Needle exchanges play a vital
OL,9,Frole in terms of people bringing their
OL,10,Fneedles back to an exchange so they're
OL,11,Fnot littered in the streets.
OL,13,F"But also, needle exchanges work
OL,14,Faround reducing HIV and reducing blood-
OL,15,Fborne viruses.
OL,17,F"So, they do a lot of work around harm
OL,18,Freduction.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1779185247
OL,3,CNeedle exchange facility plans spark
OL,4,Canti-social behaviour concerns for
OL,5,Ctraders
OL,7,F"It's also looking at that individual
OL,8,Fto try and get them off the drugs and
OL,9,Fget them into recovery.
OL,11,F"So, needle exchange is a lot more
OL,12,Fthan just providing a needle or a pack
OL,13,Fof needles for people."
OL,15,FPosters have appeared calling for
OL,16,Fpeople to attend a meeting on the
OL,17,Fissue and to raise complaints.
OL,19,FHowever, Paul does not believe this is
OL,20,Fthe way forward for those concerned.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1779185247
OL,3,CNeedle exchange facility plans spark
OL,4,Canti-social behaviour concerns for
OL,5,Ctraders
OL,7,FHe continued: "This fear initially of
OL,8,Fputting out posters and protests, come
OL,9,Fand speak to the council, come and
OL,10,Fspeak to the local reps, and those
OL,11,Fpeople who are working on the ground
OL,12,Fto try and find a solution that's
OL,13,Fgoing to work for everybody because,
OL,14,Freality is, drugs are not going to go
OL,15,Faway tomorrow. It's on the increase."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
