FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1779185247
OL,3,CNeedle exchange facility plans spark
OL,4,Canti-social behaviour concerns for
OL,5,Ctraders
OL,7,FA spokesperson from the Belfast Trust
OL,8,Fsaid: "Belfast Trust has met with
OL,9,Flocal business owners on a number of
OL,10,Foccasions to discuss concerns and
OL,11,Fprovide assurance on the core service
OL,12,Fdelivery of the Belfast Inclusion
OL,13,FHealth Service (BIHS).
OL,15,F"We remain dedicated to establishing
OL,16,Finnovative ways of working across the
OL,17,Fhealth and social care sector to
OL,18,Fimprove health outcomes for people
OL,19,Fexperiencing homelessness.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1779185247
OL,3,CNeedle exchange facility plans spark
OL,4,Canti-social behaviour concerns for
OL,5,Ctraders
OL,7,F"BIHS is a nurse-led multidisciplinary
OL,8,Fteam that provides health services to
OL,9,Fmembers of the local homelessness
OL,10,Fcommunity.
OL,12,F"These services include podiatry,
OL,13,Fdental, GP sessions and social work
OL,14,Fand can offer clean needles if
OL,15,Frequested by the user.
OL,17,F"The Trust continues to work in
OL,18,Fpartnership with all parties involved,
OL,19,Fincluding the local business
OL,20,Fcommunity."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1779185247
OL,3,CNeedle exchange facility plans spark
OL,4,Canti-social behaviour concerns for
OL,5,Ctraders
OL,7,FA Belfast City Council spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "The council recognises the need
OL,9,Ffor support services to assist our
OL,10,Fmost vulnerable residents, notes that
OL,11,Fsuch facilities are a regular feature
OL,12,Fof other modern city centres and
OL,13,Fcontinues to work closely with our
OL,14,Fstatutory and community partners to
OL,15,Fsupport those who are vulnerable.
OL,17,F"We have received correspondence from
OL,18,Flocal businesses in relation to this
OL,19,Fsite, and a meeting will be arranged
OL,20,Fbetween their representatives and
OL,21,Felected members."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
